menuconfig MALI400
	tristate "Mali-300/400/450 support"
	depends on ARM
	default y
	---help---
	This enables support for the ARM Mali-300, Mali-400, and Mali-450
	GPUs.

	To compile this driver as a module, choose M here: the module will be
	called mali.

choice
	depends on MALI400
	prompt "Select MALI VER"
